org.integratedmodelling.thinklab.api.knowledge.storage
Interface IKBoxCapabilities

public interface IKBoxCapabilities

Objects of this class are returned by IKBox.getCapabilities() to tell us what the kbox supports and doesn't. Mostly unimplemented this far.

Author:
Ferdinando Villa
